Package com.facebook.buck.jvm.java.abi

Class SourceAbiCompatibleVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
      • com.facebook.buck.jvm.java.abi.SourceAbiCompatibleVisitor
  • public class SourceAbiCompatibleVisitor
extends org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
    This class fixes up a few details of class ABIs so that they match the way source ABIs generate the same details. It allows us to take potentially risky shortcuts in source ABIs without losing the ability to verify them by binary comparison against class ABIs.
